questions: ['What are the other natural wonders of the world besides the Great Barrier Reef?', 'What licenses and permits are needed for a food truck?', 'How do you get impartial results from search engines?', 'What’s the best bike seat', 'Interesting. What was the basis of the backlash Marvel Studios faced for the Vice President’s suggestion that diversity was causing sales to slide?', 'How often should I run to lose weight?', 'What is the role of Co-Extra in GMO food traceability in the EU?', 'Tell me about the different types of rocket engines.', 'Why did the Airbus A380 stop being produced?', 'I like hiking and Malbec wine. You mentioned some high peaks. How can I hike some high mountains and visit some wineries famous for Malbec?']
answers: ["The other Natural Wonders of the World besides the Great Barrier Reef include the Grand Canyon, Northern Lights, Victoria Falls, Mt. Everest, and Paricutin Volcano. These wonders are remarkable geological features and natural phenomena created by the forces of nature over time, showcasing the Earth's diverse and awe-inspiring landscapes and events.", "The licenses and permits needed for a food truck vary by country and locality. In Toronto, Canada, requirements include business and liability insurance, a Commercial Vehicle Operator's Registration for the truck, permits for each municipality it operates in, a food handler certificate, the appropriate driver's licenses, assistant's licenses for assistants, and a health inspection, among others.", 'You can obtain impartial search results from search engines like DuckDuckGo by using platforms that do not store your personal information or track your online activities. DuckDuckGo, for example, ensures user privacy and impartiality in search results by not relying on past user data to tailor search outcomes, providing a clean and unbiased search experience.', 'Highly recommended bike seat is the Brooks England Cambium C-17 Saddle. It offers maintenance-free use, waterproof properties, and exceptional comfort for long rides. Its design, including flexibility on rough terrain and suitability for touring enthusiasts and bike packers, makes it a top choice for comfortable and versatile cycling experiences.', "The backlash against Marvel Studios was rooted in the revelation of an unpublished decision by the studio chairs to reduce diversity and prioritize the hiring of predominantly white males for future productions. This decision contradicted Marvel's earlier efforts to promote diversity in its comic books and on-screen characters. Fans and critics criticized the shift, viewing it as a step backward in terms of representation and inclusivity in the entertainment industry.", "Losing weight through running can be achieved easily as running tends to burn calories. To achieve weight loss while running, focus on decreasing your caloric intake by consuming nutrient-dense, fibre-rich foods. Additionally, incorporate strength training exercises to build muscle mass, as muscle weighs less than fat. If you're struggling to lose weight or have specific goals in mind, consider consulting a registered dietitian or a personal trainer for professional adice. They can help you create a customized nutrition and exercise plan tailored to your needs.", 'Co-Extra, an EU-funded research program, primarily focused on developing genetically modified organisms (GMOs) that could be used to enhance food traceability in the European Union. Their goal was to create GMOs with unique genetic markers that could be easily detected in food products. By introducing these GMOs into the supply chain, Co-Extra aimed to establish a foolproof traceability system, ensuring consumers could track the origin of their food accurately.', 'Rocket engines can be categorized into four main types based on their propulsion methods. Solid-fuel rockets use propellant in a solid phase, while liquid-propellant rockets rely on propellants in a liquid state fed from tanks. Hybrid rockets combine a solid propellant with a liquid or gas oxidizer, and monopropellant rockets use a single propellant decomposed by a catalyst. These different types of engines have diverse applications and performance characteristics in rocketry.', 'The Airbus A380 ceased production due to a combination of factors. Firstly, new safety tests prompted by the Malaysia Airlines Flight 17 (MH17) catastrophe raised concerns about evacuation protocols for such large aircraft. Additionally, during the COVID-19 pandemic, the reduced demand for air travel and safety regulations discouraged the use of such massive airplanes, making their production economically unviable. These factors collectively contributed to the discontinuation of the A380 program.', 'To combine hiking and Malbec wine, plan a trip to the Penedès region in Catalonia. You can explore the Montserrat mountain range, which offers fantastic hiking opportunities, and then visit renowned wineries in the Penedès, known for its exceptional Malbec wine production. This region offers a perfect blend of outdoor adventure and wine tasting experiences.']
